  "body": "### Description\nWhile attestation duties can be calculated one epoch ahead, block production duties are only stable in the epoch they actually occur in (because they use the validator effective balances which change at epoch boundaries).\n\nWe should rework the validator client to only request block production duties for the current epoch. Need to ensure we still correctly create the block for the first slot in the epoch.",
